Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特·艾娲嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然有用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,工作吧 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,分邮件困难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢您使用自动笔记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.10,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}曾是军人的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,战争已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是少佐的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 要是他不需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,应该把我处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请扔掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}开始迈上新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鸥莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你要…活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}自由地活下去
